function approximateFraction(x) {
  if (Math.floor(x) === x) {
    return [x, 1];
  }
  var xinv = 1 / x;
  var limit = 8;
  if (xinv > limit) {
    return [1, limit];
  } else if (Math.floor(xinv) === xinv) {
    return [1, xinv];
  }
  var x_ = x > 1 ? xinv : x;
  var a = 0,
      b = 1,
      c = 1,
      d = 1;
  while (true) {
    var p = a + c,
        q = b + d;
    if (q > limit) {
      break;
    }
    if (x_ <= p / q) {
      c = p;
      d = q;
    } else {
      a = p;
      b = q;
    }
  }
  var result;
  if (x_ - a / b < c / d - x_) {
    result = x_ === x ? [a, b] : [b, a];
  } else {
    result = x_ === x ? [c, d] : [d, c];

  return result;
}
